\">Marco\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Aurelio\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Aurelius\">Aurelio\u003C/span> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Tuuli Ahlholm, Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"la\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"imperial\" data-text=\"Imperatori · Caesari · Marco · Aurelio\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Imperatori\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"imperator\">IMP\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Caesari\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Caesari\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Caesar\">CAES\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Marco\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Marco\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Marcus\">M\u003C/span>\u003C/span>·\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Aurelio\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Aurelio\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Aurelius\">\u003Cspan class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">A͡U\u003C/span>..[...\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Imperatori\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"imperator\">IMPERATORI\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Caesari\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Caesar\">CAESARI\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Marco\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Marcus\">MARCO\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Aurelio\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"Aurelius\">AURELIO\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000019_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo R. Henzel, 2016-11-07\" src=\"ISic000019_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic000019.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo R. Henzel, 2016-11-07\" src=\"ISic000019-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text of ILPalermo (Bivona) checked against the photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"1\">1: \u003Cspan> Bivona: Auṛẹ; Mommsen: AV̂R \u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>As Bivona notes, Mommsen in CIL chose to unify this fragment with one recorded by Gualtherus and Fazello (ISic001896, on a piece of an architrave, re-used as a church step, and which read: IMP. M. AVRELIO . ANTONINO . AVG...). However. Torremuzza described that piece separately from this one, which he placed in the courtyard of the Palazzo Senatorio, and there seems no obvious reason to conflate them.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Castelli 1762 13 no.xxiv \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002085\" targ